item.title: CVE-2023-6562|2024-08-02T08:35:14.693Z -- kakadu%20software%20pty%20ltd -- kakadu%20sdk
item.description: JPX Fragment List (flst) box vulnerability in Kakadu 7.9 allows an attacker to exfiltrate local and remote files reachable by a server if the server allows the attacker to upload a specially-crafted the image that is displayed back to the attacker.
